name: Star vs. the Forces of Evil
original_name: Star vs. the Forces of Evil
overview: Intergalactic warrior Star Butterfly arrives on Earth to live with the Diaz family. She continues to battle villains throughout the universe and high school, mainly to protect her extremely powerful wand, an object that still confuses her.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: After having skirmished with a number of dangerous monsters, Star Butterfly arrives on Earth to live with the Diaz family. However, rather than living a normal life, Star continues on having to battle villains both throughout the universe and in their high school, although if only to protect her extremely powerful wand, an object which she is still confused with.

episodes.name: Star Comes to Earth
episodes.overview: As tradition dictates, Star receives the royal magic wand for her 14th birthday, but her parents worry that she is not ready for the responsibility and send her to a place they deem safe - Earth.

episodes.name: Party With a Pony
episodes.overview: Star's best friend from her home dimension pays a visit and feels threatened by Star's new friendship with Marco.

episodes.name: Match Maker
episodes.overview: Star fails her first test, so she tries to play match maker for their classroom teacher to get a better grade. However, she winds up turning her into a troll.

guest_stars.character: Queen Moon Butterfly / Jackie Lynn Thomas (voice)

episodes.name: The Other Exchange Student
